text: Marc-Andre Fleury starts tonight for MIN
Warmup time. Jake Oettinger leads the Stars onto the ice while Marc-Andre Fleury does the same for the Wild. Wow surprised at that one.
Loved @NanneLoua rationale for starting Fleury tonight. just didnt think theyd do it.
Full disclosure. When I said Minnesota would win tonight it was before I learned Fleury was starting.
